{"tid":508610,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]2016聖誕節由香港踩單車上廣州","createTime":"2017-12-24T12:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T15:39:25.000Z","uid":67976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48702e468eaa27cc030afc5119c8afe513204c70","tid":508610,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"由於原來我個舊post已經推極都推唔郁，喺旅遊台再搵唔返個post；加上已經死左一半圖，就真係最後開埋呢次post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡量今晚找埋條數佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實想踩單車旅行好耐，只係一直都無時間同心力。適逢sem迫，又有感情問題，唔想喪飲酒咁頹，把心一橫就決定踩單車避節，上年去伊朗都係咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n本身老母唔知我踩單車返大陸，我話去露營好幾日就過左骨，hehe。之後放左架單車起朋友屋企，費事佢問長問短<br />\n<br />\n查實我無乜點踩過公路，計埋呢次既話總共淨係踩過三次，第一次喺伊朗，第二次下白泥，第三次就係呢次。真係唔知那兒來的勇氣<br />\n<br />\n由大窩口到廣州市中心都係二百幾km，其實唔難(好似係)<br />\n<br />\n朝早去完朋友屋企拎車就出發，諗住大窩口踩去上水再轉火車過關<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/195900_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F195900_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e28c345e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/200135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F200135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ccb2d025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n途中經過母校好感概 打返個卡先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/200227_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F200227_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=afe168c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當踩到大埔道上斜果陣竟然踩唔到要落車推一陣，其實差少少就到頂，不過人生既野...雖然未出香港已經要推車，不過其實之後全程都無推過。或者真係開始好難，過左就無野難到你。"},{"pid":"7927f5060fece9ce74ec2412defa8e00db1e891c","tid":508610,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201023_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201023_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1d52f357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多馬騮 影果陣幾驚佢會搶我部電話黎食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=74c6c0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當踩到沙田果陣開始feel到啲行李鬆鬆地，落車一睇原來斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後即刻去單車公園買返條內胎黎綁。去左鴻運單車鋪，個老細唔收我錢仲幫我綁埋，好撚感動，佢淨係話叫多啲人黎租車就得喇，識玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扺我之前每次黎租單車都淨係搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6d25e5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踩到晏晝先記得自己乜都無食過，就去左大埔食野，但真係幾難食sosad 又唔係平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係因為呢個位睇到我部單車我都唔會食，香港真係好多偷車撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201356_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fb83a4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完野同hea左陣就踩去上水，去到果條踩唔到單車既單車徑就行去地鐵站，拆轆入閘過深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201543_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201543_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ed08cee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過到黎先發現唔記得喺香港買sim卡，唯有喺大陸買，但屌佢老母80蚊人仔得500mb，仲要我攞住張回鄉證on99咁比佢影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最少有得用好過無得用啦，感謝党<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201921_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201921_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=04139fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見天都黑又唔想踩夜車就喺度落腳，最尾搵左間賓館90蚊人仔，諗住第一晚就住豪少少啦。入左房安頓好之後包租婆突然敲我門，問我要唔要女，我果陣嚇左一嚇，乜你咁直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴打上去玩過其實係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾落街食左好多野就返上房，反而呢一晚我唔係太訓得著，可能唔相信自己真係踩左上黎，同埋聽日就踩大陸既路，唔多唔少都有啲緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/201952_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F201952_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3614ba1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二日起身食埋個唔扺食既早餐就check out踩去東莞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23466cc253d52c6981fb941e1d803f58a9c0682","tid":508610,"uid":120216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"舊POST有印象 LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4000fa7a7e2edd3acc955d00747d248218d5a419","tid":508610,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"好似果位巴打行路上先勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}